# VERSION
v0.16.2

# Changelog
- v0.16.2
    - Added non-export in telemetry component
- v0.16.1
    - Allow all origins and common methods/headers in http server
- v0.16.0
    - Added postgresql GORM component.
- v0.15.5
    - Documentation updated: Added diagrams for arch/components/sequences...
    - BUT not finished yet.
- v0.15.4
    - Mysql GORM component support auto-migration when starting.
- v0.15.3
    - Edit doc from chapter 1 to chapter 10.
- v0.15.2
    - infra/go/application/registry/registry.go Simplification:
        - Remove RegisterWithDeps and RegisterAutoInferName, keep only Register (with explicit name) and a new RegisterAuto (which automatically infers name and dependencies).
        - Simplify the Builder struct to only include: Name, Fn, Auto, Deps, and caching fields; remove any redundant flags.
        - Construction flow: pre-build automatic components -> infer tag-based dependencies -> perform topological sorting -> register.
- v0.15.1
    - Added deduplication in autowire process.
    - Added flag "auto" and dependency inferencing in registry.
- v0.15.0
    - Added tag-based dependencies injection, autowired and don't need to inject manually.
- v0.14.0
    - Added support for user-declared runtime dependencies.
    - TODO: support auto-injection of dependencies in components.
- v0.13.2
    - Added dumpRoutes in HTTP SERVER component for debugging purpose.
- v0.13.1
    - Added HTTP SERVER Component usage example in Documents.
- v0.13.0
    - Added extendable component by adding registry builders.
    - Also provided ability for dynamic customized component.
    - Added ProvideComponent directly.
    - Supplied dependencies for mysql component and gorm component.
    - Doc also updated.
- v0.12.0
    - Changed OS vars to flag arguments.
    - Added biz config support in config manager and app, also provide new Exportable func to users.
- v0.11.7
    - Added stop log for open telemetry component.
    - Temporarily removed runEnhanced() in app.go.
- v0.11.6
    - Remove ServiceName from HTTPServerConfig
    - Use APPName as ServiceName
    - Added traceparent in http server/client component
    - Added http client demo in main.go and config.yaml
- v0.11.5
    - Change name of logging out put file to "{appname}.log.20250101"
    - HTTP server/client componet removed "trace_id" and use w3c standard trace
- v0.11.4
    - Adjuested grpc server/client component to make compatible with otel & logging.
    - Added README.md for grpc server/client component.
- v0.11.3
    - Added InstallWindowsCtrlHandler for non-windows platform to avoid build error.
- v0.11.2
    - Fixed bug of cannot stopAll(); App.Shutdown will not call stopAll() when need to shutdown.
- v0.11.1
    - Design of "TraceID" changed to industry in logging component.
    - Added "span_id" in logging component.
    - Renamed filename such as "*_component.go" in each component folder to "component.go" to keep it unified.
- v0.11.0
    - Added doc: "Infrastructure of Go"
- v0.10.4
  - Refactored the components registration logic in app.go
  - Updated shutdown Run() logic to support different platforms.
- v0.10.3
  - Fixed unused global hook manager
  - Replace hard code consts "grpc_clients" in component registration with consts in consts package.
  - Added err check in Telemetry registration.
  - Fixed repeated signal management code in application.
  - Provided gorm component an individual config rather than using mysql config.
  - Updated logic in starting failure handling.
- v0.10.2
  - Updated go mod version
- v0.10.1
  - Change Go version to 1.23.0
- v0.10.0
